divs: Sighting Details#1 In my yard sitting in a chair looking up at the beautiful sky. #2 the flashing pulsating silver lite. #3 Thought it was a plane or helicopter, but I think not. #4 Moving slowly, very high almost hovering, to slow for a plane and to high for a helicopter. Pulsating very regular. #5 I had no feeling one way or the other about the event #6 I looked away for about 15 seconds because my neck was begining to hurt looked back to try and re locate it but it was gone.
